{"type":null,"faqId":11977,"title":"G620-L72  手机自动关机或重启，如何解决？","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机自动关机或重启，若是可拆卸电池，可能是由于电池接触不良造成。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请取下电池后，使用棉布蘸取酒精擦拭电池和手机上的触点，重装电池后开机</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，长按电源键打开选项菜单，选择“重新启动”。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法打开选项菜单，请长按电源键</span><span> 10 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">秒以上，强制重启。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若重启后仍然出现问题，可能是由于某些第三方应用程序不兼容。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">建议备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法操作手机，请将手机强制升级。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包，参考软件升级包中的升级指导操作。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">进入</span><span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/service-center/index.htm</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">查询全国服务网点；</span> <span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">或关注华为终端官方微信平台：华为终端（微信号：</span><span>huaweizhongduan</span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">），在对话界面，点击“自助服务</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">服务中心查询”根据屏幕提示查询离您最近的服务网点。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如您接收到官网推送的版本升级通知，请及时在线升级，以体验更好的手机性能。</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2760","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398822379000,"seriesProductName":"G620-L72","visitedTimes":757,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"重启","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}